<h3 id="creating-radio-buttons">Creating Radio Buttons</h3>

<p>If you want some multiple-choice questions, you can use a checkbox but you‚Äôre better off with radio buttons. Set them up like this, it‚Äôs a blast!</p>

<div class="mdl-typography--text-center">
  <img src="/images/community/tutorials/reg-radio-buttons.gif" width="400px" />
